{"tid":991025,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"WhatsApp限轉發5次　防謠言散播","createTime":"2019-01-22T05:26:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T06:20:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e5910d29f980f41be4e7b90adb0bc0980c9d78a1","tid":991025,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T05:26:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190122/20596429\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190122%2F20596429&d=hvi0Gj61P2aDcx%2Bz4nMIpzANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=74669d7a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190122%2F20596429&h=4726ba97\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190122/20596429</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年01月22日 <br />\n<br />\nWhatsApp限轉發5次　防謠言散播<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190122/large/15235102.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190122%2Flarge%2F15235102.jpg&h=95635d55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nWhatsApp昨宣佈推出新措施，限制用戶轉發同一段文字給最多五個用戶或群組。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在全球擁有15億用戶的即時通訊程式WhatsApp昨日宣佈推出新措施，限制用戶轉發同一段文字給最多五個用戶或群組，以遏止謠言散播；不過，昨晚本報記者在香港測試，仍可多次轉發連結和文字給多於五個用戶。<br />\n<br />\nWhatsApp因為以安全加密形式傳送短訊、相片和影片而廣為人用，原先它設定用戶可轉發同一篇訊息250次，及至去年印度發生多宗經WhatsApp瘋傳流言、煽動暴民施襲的命案和傷人案，為遏止暴行，程式半年前限制印度用戶轉發短訊次數，每篇只可發給五個用戶或群組，全球其他用戶則限於20次。<br />\n<br />\n在昨日印尼耶加達一個活動上，WhatsApp政策及通訊副總裁格蘭德（Victoria Grand）公佈轉發訊息五次的限制擴至全球用戶，並稱即時執行。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同一訊息最多傳1,280用戶<br />\n<br />\n以每個群組最多可有256個用戶計算，即同一個訊息最多只可轉發給1,280個用戶，較現時5,120個大幅減少。<br />\n<br />\n不過不同手機平台更新時間有先後之分，據知Android用戶會先更新，稍後才到iOS用戶。不過本報記者昨晚分別以Android手機和iPhone的最新版本WhatsApp測試轉發功能，仍然可多次轉發新聞連結及訊息給超過五個用戶，不清楚新例會否按地區逐步更新。WhatsApp亦未明言若用戶轉發五次後複製訊息再轉發，系統是否能夠偵測得到內容是轉發過的「舊文」。<br />\n<br />\n路透社／本報記者  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n民建聯藉機收集街坊資料<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n躁鬱症衞署女助理控上司歧視"},{"pid":"6bce2e9d487ca03d81d8180737a7a739f9d9f160","tid":991025,"uid":21002,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T05:53:42.000Z","msg":"癈老傳五癈老再五次方一直上"},{"pid":"659b0b7041e763e5e9a85995d4793843ed694c86","tid":991025,"uid":183219,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:00:11.000Z","msg":"唔撚用wts傳咪得lor 屌"},{"pid":"e720c4e81deb311f5d6073e208bb1c9c25857fc2","tid":991025,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:01:19.000Z","msg":"如果加一粒標點符號？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c59aaf9e383987fd766265185e3a6ca3c2bdcefe","tid":991025,"uid":101328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:04:38.000Z","msg":"有時send d過是過節野都要分好多次send...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9087323a70ab1aafe5fb43ebb91152ddae0d26e5","tid":991025,"uid":37232,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:09:50.000Z","msg":"德政"},{"pid":"7d7766cef1e9ff4d07b19c0e280724588df18db2","tid":991025,"uid":9286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6bce2e9d487ca03d81d8180737a7a739f9d9f160","tid":991025,"uid":21002,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T05:53:42.000Z","msg":"癈老傳五癈老再五次方一直上"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:19:08.000Z","msg":"廢老用開wechat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7553d7866b9e7cf34f2b0b45ca6d644d2abda157","tid":991025,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:20:02.000Z","msg":"你限死內容農場名單唔比forward ，copy會唔會好d"},{"pid":"79544ceaa2a0a69c95593bdc422e973d7619d7a4","tid":991025,"uid":142233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:20:06.000Z","msg":"copy n paste咪得囉"}]}